plugins.description: A plugin that allows you to save, manage, and follow coordinates with ease.

usage.description: Adds coordinates to the list. Use `add` to add your current coordinates.
Deletes coordinates from the list. Use `del <n>` to delete the coordinate at position `n`. Use `del` without parameters to delete the last coordinate in the list.
Saves or loads the coordinate list to/from an encrypted file. Files are saved as `name.coords`. Files are encrypted using a password (`pass`).
